00:22:56.070 --> 00:23:00.040
Providing equal access to
the arts requires input

00:23:00.040 --> 00:23:05.100
at every level -- parents,
teachers, local, state,

00:23:05.100 --> 00:23:08.140
national leaders,
principals, superintendents,

00:23:08.140 --> 00:23:11.350
