the arts as a fundamental

00:23:15.170 --> 00:23:18.780
and indispensable part of
our children's success.

00:23:18.780 --> 00:23:21.520
Because arts education
is not about --

00:23:21.520 --> 00:23:25.500
just about children learning how
to finger a B flat on a trumpet.

00:23:25.500 --> 00:23:28.680
That might be nice, but it's
not just about learning how

00:23:28.680 --> 00:23:31.640
to pirouette, although
that might be nice.

00:23:31.640 --> 00:23:33.790
Or teaching children
how to use watercolors

00:23:33.790 --> 00:23:35.470
to paint a picture of a tree.

00:23:35.470 --> 00:23:37.230
That might be nice.

00:23:37.230 --> 00:23:42.140
Arts education is about giving
students a tool belt of skills

00:23:42.140 --> 00:23:45.210
that allow them to reach
their full potential,

00:23:45.210 --> 00:23:49.000
where children can achieve
academically and socially,

00:23:49.000 --> 00:23:52.490
and where they can imagine a
world beyond what they might

00:23:52.490 --> 00:23:57.060
know, and dream of new
possibilities for themselves,

00:23:57.060 --> 00:24:00.500
and where they can express their
ideas beyond the use of linear,

00:24:00.500 --> 00:24:02.280
everyday conversations.

00:24:02.280 --> 00:24:05.350
And they can develop
self-confidence, and discover

00:24:05.350 --> 00:24:09.510
that they really do belong,
and communicate with others,

00:24:09.510 --> 00:24:12.340
and reach those who have
perspectives different

00:24:12.340 --> 00:24:16.620
from their own, and
innovate, and create.

00:24:16.620 --> 00:24:19.650
Because we know that whenever
we create, we move away

00:24:19.650 --> 00:24:23.450
from being stuck, and we open
the door to solving those old

00:24:23.450 --> 00:24:29.160
and tired problems in new, and
positive, and meaningful ways.

00:24:29.160 --> 00:24:32.820
The United States has always
been a nation of innovators

00:24:32.820 --> 00:24:35.740
and visionaries, and
instilling the arts

00:24:35.740 --> 00:24:39.230
in our students will help ensure

00:24:39.230 --> 00:24:41.530
