00:52:40.630 --> 00:52:43.230
in Brookland/Edgewood
for 31 years.

00:52:43.230 --> 00:52:45.600
Our Founding Director
Carla Perlo

00:52:45.600 --> 00:52:48.360
and her Co-Director Deborah
Riley recently retired,

00:52:48.360 --> 00:52:50.210
