been too jarring.

00:53:50.660 --> 00:53:52.950
So what's happened in
our neighborhood is

00:53:52.950 --> 00:53:56.970
that our community has continued
to mix both economically,

00:53:56.970 --> 00:54:01.120
racially, and in all kind
of definitions of diversity.

00:54:01.120 --> 00:54:03.460
So that's presented Dance Place

00:54:03.460 --> 00:54:04.830
with some wonderful
opportunities

00:54:04.830 --> 00:54:07.970
in our different programs
to engage the community,

00:54:07.970 --> 00:54:11.290
to bring them in, and see
