01:11:35.710 --> 01:11:39.220
He is a jazz pianist.

01:11:39.220 --> 01:11:40.800
He is a composer.

01:11:40.800 --> 01:11:44.480
He is just an incredible
musician.

01:11:44.480 --> 01:11:48.700
And he really -- his work
exemplifies what I am talking

01:11:48.700 --> 01:11:55.080
about, which is how does music
act as an individual voice?

01:11:55.080 --> 01:11:58.350
How do you create it so
that it is your voice?

01:11:58.350 --> 01:12:02.930
And so I'm going to turn it
