01:43:16.730 --> 01:43:18.260
Not necessarily Asperger's,

01:43:18.260 --> 01:43:22.070
but kind of in the
medium of the spectrum.

01:43:22.070 --> 01:43:23.370
&gt;&gt; Mario Rossero: Great.

