development.

02:11:33.940 --> 02:11:35.580
We test them and we develop

02:11:35.580 --> 02:11:36.880
through our professional
development.

02:11:36.880 --> 02:11:39.160
And we're going to have some
examples of those on tables

02:11:39.160 --> 02:11:42.650
