grab one, you're welcome to it.

02:11:42.650 --> 02:11:44.960
We also try to provide
everything as much

02:11:44.960 --> 02:11:48.530
as what we do online for
free to a national audience.

02:11:48.530 --> 02:11:51.310
And so we have two vehicles
for our web presence

02:11:51.310 --> 02:11:52.690
which I'll talk about later.

02:11:52.690 --> 02:11:54.720
And then we have a coaching
