So we can look at, you
know, choreographic notes

02:14:29.590 --> 02:14:31.970
that the Library has a
beautiful collection of

02:14:31.970 --> 02:14:36.640
or musical notation or notes
from a dramateur or sketchbooks

02:14:36.640 --> 02:14:37.960
or notes of an artist.

02:14:37.960 --> 02:14:41.940
And so those are all the reasons
why we think it's important.

02:14:41.940 --> 02:14:43.890
So the way that we
developed our program is

02:14:43.890 --> 02:14:45.700
that we have two
different types of courses

02:14:45.700 --> 02:14:47.000
and I've listed these here.

