And the overview
courses generally are

02:14:59.030 --> 02:15:00.330
about 40 to 45 [inaudible].

02:15:00.330 --> 02:15:03.240
It depends and they're very
field trip and lecture-based.

02:15:03.240 --> 02:15:04.600
We don't do that much hands on.

02:15:04.600 --> 02:15:05.900
We do a little bit.

02:15:05.900 --> 02:15:08.290
And then the discipline-specific
course is do more

02:15:08.290 --> 02:15:09.970
