in the discipline.

02:15:09.970 --> 02:15:11.480
So I'm just going to just
talk a little bit first

02:15:11.480 --> 02:15:13.280
about our overview of courses.

02:15:13.280 --> 02:15:14.830
So in those courses
-- oh, by the way --

02:15:14.830 --> 02:15:17.930
