We get teachers from
across the country,

02:15:26.380 --> 02:15:29.320
people from San Francisco,
people -- because they're free,

02:15:29.320 --> 02:15:31.020
sometimes teachers will
use it as an opportunity

02:15:31.020 --> 02:15:32.320
to get to Philadelphia.

02:15:32.320 --> 02:15:35.390
We can help them find, you
