02:15:42.050 --> 02:15:43.490
And I think what
we were surprised

02:15:43.490 --> 02:15:45.560
to learn is how many people

02:15:45.560 --> 02:15:47.710
that take our classes
don't actually know

02:15:47.710 --> 02:15:50.720
about the digitized collections
of the Library of Congress

02:15:50.720 --> 02:15:55.810
in any subject matter, let alone
the Library, let alone the arts.

02:15:55.810 --> 02:15:57.720
So that's really sort of
an opportunity for them

02:15:57.720 --> 02:15:59.460
to get comfortable
with their searches

02:15:59.460 --> 02:16:01.990
and understands a little
bit about the framework.

